	KALAH GAME PROTOCOL

This is a fork to https://github.com/KWARC/kalah-game/tree/trunk
It extends the original repository with implementations for MiniMax- and MCTS-clients.

Contents of this repository:

  /spec/	The source of a specification, of a protocol to
  		play Kalah.

  /server/	A collection of server implementations, of the
  		protocol.

  /client/	A collection of client-side libraries, which
  		implement the protocol.

  /misc/	Utility programs and scripts

The project homepage can be found here:

    https://github.com/KWARC/kalah-game
